<section class="py-20" id="faq">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Questions, answered</h2>
      <p class="text-muted text-lg">We build for transparency. Here are the top things families ask before joining.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <article class="bg-surface p-7 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Can I pause sharing anytime?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Yes. A single tap pauses updates instantly, and you can schedule automatic quiet hours.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="bg-surface p-7 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Which devices work with HorizonLink?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">Any Android phone for sharing. Receivers can use Android TV, Android mobile, or Google Assistant at launch.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="bg-surface p-7 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">How do you keep data secure?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">All data is encrypted in transit and at rest. Only approved devices with explicit consent can access updates.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
